entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`sessionId` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, `dateId` INTEGER NOT NULL, `sessionHeading` TEXT NOT NULL, `sessionLogs` INTEGER NOT NULL)
CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`sessionHeading` TEXT NOT NULL, content=`SessionDto`)
contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_SessionDtoFts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `SessionDto` BEGIN DELETE FROM `SessionDtoFts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_SessionDtoFts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `SessionDto` BEGIN DELETE FROM `SessionDtoFts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_SessionDtoFts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `SessionDto` BEGIN INSERT INTO `SessionDtoFts`(`docid`, `sessionHeading`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`sessionHeading`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_SessionDtoFts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `SessionDto` BEGIN INSERT INTO `SessionDtoFts`(`docid`, `sessionHeading`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`sessionHeading`); END
